42:37.781 --> 42:48.012
The reason I have what I modestly feel is the greatest dick inflection in the world is not through my efforts or penance, but through the efforts of a man named Kenyon Starling.

42:48.292 --> 42:49.213
Do you know that name?

42:49.354 --> 42:49.554
No.

42:50.515 --> 42:57.302
Well, all the book dealers old enough to know it, and you'd have to be in the business 10 years.

42:57.738 --> 42:59.540
No, Kenyon Starling.

42:59.561 --> 43:06.290
Kenyon Starling was a gentleman from Dayton, Ohio, and I am from Dayton, Ohio.

43:07.251 --> 43:23.914
And at the Sudanese sale in London, which was a major Dickens sale, Peggy and I went to London with our modest budget of what we wanted to buy from the Sudanese sale.

43:24.957 --> 43:28.901
We did not get, I don't think, a single item that was my first choice.

43:28.921 --> 43:31.203
We bought a few items, nice items.

