So I finally said to someone, who's Lou Feldman bidding for?

43:41.834 --> 43:44.116
And he said, he's bidding for a guy from Dayton, Ohio.

43:44.377 --> 43:45.818
I said, I'm from Dayton, Ohio.

43:46.959 --> 43:48.741
And he said, well, this guy's a recluse.

