And as you do, after we were ready to leave, we said, well, Mr. Starling, if you ever get to Los Angeles, look us up.

45:45.138 --> 45:47.861
We'd love to show you my library.

45:47.881 --> 45:48.181
We'd say, fine.

45:48.221 --> 45:49.503
People never do, but we'd say fine.

