47:34.115 --> 47:38.078
And I said, well, I know you wouldn't buy it, because he was such a sticker on condition.

47:38.359 --> 47:41.241
He wouldn't buy anything that wasn't terrific.

47:41.261 --> 47:43.824
And I said, you wouldn't buy it, but I haven't got it.

47:44.044 --> 47:44.504
You have.

