49:06.729 --> 49:10.934
As Bill said, he had no brothers and sisters.

49:11.014 --> 49:11.455
Nobody.

49:11.955 --> 49:14.999
And none of his friends were interested in book collecting.

49:15.019 --> 49:17.783
People he had, friends that were art collectors and whatnot.

49:18.134 --> 49:20.217
And we, so we loved.

