And he said, sure, come in.

50:18.784 --> 50:21.206
We'll have dinner tomorrow night, which was a Friday night.

50:21.226 --> 50:31.237
So, I flew in on Friday, and we always had a drink of scotch in the library, and a friend of us had come over and inherited his shoes.

