He said, no, no, we're going to go to dinner.

50:47.839 --> 50:49.342
He said, let's rest.

50:49.362 --> 50:49.883
In Paris.

50:50.864 --> 50:51.425
In Paris.

50:52.306 --> 50:52.486
Oh.

